quote.summary: Qingdao Gon Technology Co Ltd is a China-based company primarily engaged in the production and manufacturing of new chemical materials. The Company operates through three segments. The Chemical Industry segment focuses on research, development, production, and sales of green petrochemical materials, organic polymer modified materials, and organic polymer composite materials. The products are used in the chemical, new energy, automotive, home appliance, and other industries. The Health Industry segment focuses on research, development, production, and sales of gelatin, collagen, and their extensions. The products are used in beauty, medical aesthetics, and new materials applications and other industries. The Company also engages in the lease of investment properties through Property Investment segment. The Company operates in both domestic and overseas markets.
